name: "Weird Thing" by Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool)
description: [Digital drawing created with a free app on my phone.] This is an artificial demon developed in a hidden lab at Henpeck University in Henpeck, Washington. It's been spotted nearly a dozen times around campus, and was once caught in the act of selling insurance to a foreign exchange student! (Evil.) ---Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool)
